# Documentation Standards

## Important Files Reference

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `.env` | Active environment configuration (git-ignored) |
| `.env.example` | Template for .env (committed) |
| `Dockerfile.template` | Docker build template (committed) |
| `docker-compose.template.yml` | Docker Compose template (committed) |
| `Dockerfile` | Generated Docker build (git-ignored) |
| `docker-compose.yml` | Generated Docker Compose (git-ignored) |
| `docker-entrypoint.sh` | Container startup script |
| `scripts/env-validate.sh` | Environment validation |
| `scripts/cli.sh` | Command-line interface |
| `scripts/menu.sh` | Interactive menu |
| `scripts/docker-generate.sh` | Template generation |
| `scripts/azure-provision-infra.sh` | Azure resource creation |
| `scripts/azure-teardown-infra.sh` | Azure resource deletion |
| `scripts/azure-validate-resources.sh` | Azure resource validation |
| `docs/ENV_GUIDE.md` | Environment variable documentation |
| `docs/SCRIPTS_GUIDE.md` | Scripts documentation |
| `docs/DOCKER_GUIDE.md` | Docker build & deployment guide |
| `docs/MIGRATION_PROVISIONING_GUIDE.md` | Complete deployment walkthrough |

## Documentation Update Triggers

When making changes, ensure relevant docs are updated:

| Change Type | Update These Docs |
|-------------|-------------------|
| Add/modify .env variable | `docs/ENV_GUIDE.md`, `.env.example` |
| Add/modify script | `docs/SCRIPTS_GUIDE.md`, `scripts/cli.sh`, `scripts/menu.sh` |
| Change Docker templates | `docs/DOCKER_GUIDE.md` |
| Change Docker build process | `docs/DOCKER_GUIDE.md` |
| Change Azure resources | `docs/MIGRATION_PROVISIONING_GUIDE.md` Section 4 |
| Change mount configuration | `docs/MIGRATION_PROVISIONING_GUIDE.md` Section 5 |
| Add architecture diagrams | `docs/mermaid/` (store .mmd source files) |

## README.md Updates

The README.md should reflect:
- Current architecture and approach
- Links to detailed documentation
- Visual diagrams (use Mermaid or ASCII art consistently)
- Updated workflow diagrams when processes change
